**Query #1**

    SELECT sales_channel, SUM(amount) AS revenue
    FROM clinic_sales
    WHERE datetime LIKE '2021%'
    GROUP BY sales_channel;

| sales_channel | revenue |
| ------------- | ------- |
| online        | 21000.0 |
| offline       | 15000.0 |

