**Query #2**

    -- 2nd
    SELECT uid, SUM(amount) AS total_spent
    FROM clinic_sales
    WHERE datetime LIKE '2021%'
    GROUP BY uid
    ORDER BY total_spent DESC
    LIMIT 10;

| uid | total_spent |
| --- | ----------- |
| u1  | 13000.0     |
| u2  | 13000.0     |
