**Query #3**

    -- 3rd
    SELECT 
        DATE_FORMAT(s.datetime, '%Y-%m') AS month,
        SUM(s.amount) AS revenue,
        SUM(e.amount) AS expense,
        SUM(s.amount) - SUM(e.amount) AS profit
    FROM clinic_sales s
    LEFT JOIN expenses e 
        ON DATE_FORMAT(s.datetime, '%Y-%m') = DATE_FORMAT(e.datetime, '%Y-%m')
    GROUP BY DATE_FORMAT(s.datetime, '%Y-%m');

| month   | revenue | expense | profit  |
| ------- | ------- | ------- | ------- |
| 2021-10 | 36000.0 | 15000.0 | 21000.0 |
| 2021-11 | 36000.0 | 10000.0 | 26000.0 |

