**Query #4**

    -- 4th 
    SELECT 
        c.city, 
        c.clinic_name, 
        SUM(s.amount) AS revenue
    FROM clinic_sales s
    JOIN clinics c ON s.cid = c.cid
    GROUP BY c.city, c.clinic_name
    ORDER BY c.city, revenue DESC;

| city   | clinic_name | revenue |
| ------ | ----------- | ------- |
| Delhi  | Clinic C    | 8000.0  |
| Mumbai | Clinic B    | 16000.0 |
| Pune   | Clinic A    | 12000.0 |

